#center.span-13.append-1
  %h2{:style => "margin-bottom: 10px"} Welcome to Call Congress!
  .welcome
    %p
      %strong When's the last time you talked to your Senator or Representative's office? 
      Is there an issue you care about that Congress isn't addressing? Do you have a question about someone's position on an issue? 
      %strong You need to Call Congress.
    %p
      When you use Call Congress to contact a Congressperson, 
      %strong a recording of the call is automatically posted online for everyone to hear. 
      Don't want the call to be recorded? You can still use the site to get contact info for your Senators and Representative.
    %p
      %strong So start now.
      %a{:href => "/register"} Register for an account
      and
      %a{:href => "/legislators"} Find a Legislator
      to call. It's that easy.

